                <div id="main">
                    <h1>Math games for kids</h1>

                    <p><B>2+2 math for kids</B> is a&nbsp;freeware program aimed to help children's education in the area of basic mathematical skills. Thanks to the program, the child learns how to count, compare numbers, add, subtract, multiply, and divide.</p>
                    <p>
                        Interesting exercises, intuitive usage, beautiful music, attractive graphics and lovable narration make children return to learn mathematics with pleasure.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        2+2 math for kids can be used for individual lessons as also at school.
                    </p>

                    <h2>Screenshots</h2>
                    <p class="images">
                        <a href="https://funnymathforkids.com/_sites/2p2/v1/images/screen01b.gif" rel="lightbox[screenschoot]"><img src="https://funnymathforkids.com/_sites/2p2/v1/images/screen01.gif" alt="" ></a>
